snippet.title: Meghan Markle & Prince Harry Don't Regret How Royal Exit Played Out
snippet.description:
Meghan Markle and Prince Harry are at peace with their transition away from life as working royals. When "Finding Freedom" co-author Omid Scobie asked friends of the couple if the pair regretted how things played out, he got a resounding answer. "The answer from everyone was no regrets whatsoever," he told Access Hollywood. "Ultimately, that world that they built for themselves in the U.S. is working for them."
